"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-amber-rutter-b1174670.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Amber Rutter has won a silver medal in theOlympics 2024women's skeet shooting final in Chateauroux.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just over three months after giving birth to her son Tommy,Team GB's Rutter kept her cool during a tense six-athlete shoot-off to seal her place in the gold medal showdown.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999381238941, \"rank\": 3.507602191593413e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter is the first British women to win a medal at theOlympic Gamesin skeet.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9587447739451006, \"rank\": 0.02312801170362471, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Rutter and Chile's Francesca Crovetto both missed one of their subsequent 10 shots, it forced a sudden-death shoot-off.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_under-20_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6443110854406116, \"rank\": 0.4127006797305151, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_under-20_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_under-20_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesca_da_Rimini\", \"score\": 0.9989617449221192, \"rank\": 0.000999238127581166, \"text\": \"Francesca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesca_da_Rimini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francesca_da_Rimini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both competitors missed one in the first six shots of the shoot-off, then a second miss from Rutter - which she strongly protested - ensured victory for Crovetto.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Replays appeared to show Rutter had hit the target, although officials said not.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, her silver medal capped a remarkable career resurgence for Rutter, who had missed out on a place at the Tokyo Games due to a positive Covid test.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Covid test\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_testing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youth